songs.title: Fire In My Lungs*
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Juice Wrld & Young Thug]
Want some more
I'm down on the floor
Pills got me down on the floor
ATL Jacob want some more nigga

[Chorus: Juice Wrld]
Fire in my lungs it's hard for me to talk
Poison words on my tongue it almost fell out again
Codeine in my cup its hard me for me to walk
Mix it with the pills I almost fell out again
Don't know when and where these demons came from
Don't know when and where but all my demons staring
Don't know when and where these demons came from
Don't know when and where but all my demons staring

[Verse 1: Juice Wrld]
Uh-huh late night out late night out right back down
Numb my pain my drugs are things money power
Know these niggas are not my pals
But I'm back now its fake smiles
Snakes turn to hissing, how
Uh yeah I must be the chosen one
